query:
SELECT 
                    customer_id,
                    COUNT(*) as total_workflows,
                    AVG(LENGTH(name)) as avg_name_length,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN state = "Active" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as active_count
                  FROM workflows
                  GROUP BY customer_id
